sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant KAP as kube-auth-proxy<br/>4180/TCP HTTP or 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Upstream as Upstream App<br/>configurable HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 1: OIDC Authentication (auth mode)
    User->>KAP: GET /protected-resource<br/>No session cookie
    KAP->>User: 302 Redirect to /oauth2/start
    User->>KAP: GET /oauth2/start
    KAP->>User: 302 Redirect to OIDC Provider
    User->>OIDC: Login with credentials<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    OIDC->>User: 302 Redirect with auth code
    User->>KAP: GET /oauth2/callback?code=xxx<br/>OAuth2 Authorization Code
    KAP->>OIDC: POST /token (Client Credentials + Auth Code)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>KAP: ID Token + Access Token
    KAP->>KAP: Validate ID Token, Create Session
    KAP->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>X-Forwarded-User, X-Forwarded-Email
    Upstream-->>KAP: Response
    KAP-->>User: Response + Set-Cookie (session)

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 2: OpenShift OAuth (auth mode)
    User->>KAP: GET /protected-resource
    KAP->>User: 302 Redirect to OpenShift OAuth
    User->>OSAuth: Login with OpenShift credentials<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    OSAuth->>User: 302 Redirect with auth code
    User->>KAP: GET /oauth2/callback?code=xxx
    KAP->>OSAuth: POST /token<br/>Client ID + Secret + Auth Code
    OSAuth-->>KAP: Access Token
    KAP->>OSAuth: GET /apis/user.openshift.io/v1/users/~<br/>Bearer Token
    OSAuth-->>KAP: User Info
    KAP->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>X-Forwarded-User, X-Forwarded-Email
    Upstream-->>KAP: Response
    KAP-->>User: Response + Set-Cookie

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 3: RBAC Proxy (rbac mode, port 8443)
    participant Client as API Client
    participant KRP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Client->>KRP: Request with Bearer Token or X.509 cert<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS 1.2+
    KRP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview (authenticate)<br/>HTTPS/443 SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>KRP: User Identity
    KRP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview (authorize)<br/>HTTPS/443 SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>KRP: Allowed/Denied
    KRP->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>x-remote-user, x-remote-groups
    Upstream-->>KRP: Response
    KRP-->>Client: Response

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 4: K8s SA Token Validation (auth mode)
    participant SA as Service Account Client
    SA->>KAP: Request with Bearer SA Token<br/>4180/TCP or 443/TCP
    KAP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview API<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>KAP: Token Valid + User Info
    KAP->>Upstream: Forward Request<br/>X-Forwarded-User
    Upstream-->>KAP: Response
    KAP-->>SA: Response
